1. *Beli* automobil za mene je bila prava luksuzna stavka. (Buying a car for me was a true luxury item.)
2. Ona je jako voljela da *beli* knjige. (She really loved to buy books.)
3. Ona je na kraju shvatila da je neophodno da *beli* novu haljinu. (In the end, she realized it was necessary to buy a new dress.)
4. Uvek sam bio zadovoljan kada bih *belio* nove stvari. (I was always happy when I would buy new things.)
5. Oni su *belili* poklone za svoju decu. (They bought gifts for their children.)
6. Mogu da ti kupim nešto ako želiš da *beliš* nešto. (I can buy you something if you want to buy something.)